    "body": "### Problem\n\n`vim.on_key` with a discard action **does not** trigger the `CursorMovedI` or `TextChangedI` events when used alone. \n\nHowever, combining it with `vim.api.nvim_buf_set_text` in the callback **may trigger these events**, even when `eventignore` is set.\n\n### x.lua for testing\n```lua\nvim.api.nvim_create_autocmd({ 'TextChangedI' }, {\n    group = vim.api.nvim_create_augroup('TextChangedIAAA', { clear = true }),\n    pattern = '*',\n    callback = function(args)\n        print('TextChanged-' .. os.date('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S'))\n    end,\n})\nvim.api.nvim_create_autocmd({ 'CursorMovedI' }, {\n    group = vim.api.nvim_create_augroup('CursorMovedIVVV', { clear = true }),\n    pattern = '*',\n    callback = function(args)\n        print('CursorMoved-' .. os.date('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S'))\n    end,\n})\n\nlocal function ignoreevent_wrap(fx)\n    local eventignore = vim.o.eventignore\n    vim.o.eventignore = 'all'\n\n    local ret = nil\n    if fx then\n        ret = fx()\n    end\n\n    vim.o.eventignore = eventignore\n    return ret\nend\n\n\nvim.on_key(function(key)\n    if vim.api.nvim_get_mode().mode == 'i' then\n        if key == 'a' then\n            ignoreevent_wrap(function()\n                vim.api.nvim_buf_set_text(0, 0, 0, 0, 0, { 'aaa' })\n            end)\n            return ''\n        end\n    end\nend)\n```\n\n### y.lua will not trigger.\n```lua\nvim.on_key(function(key)\n    if vim.api.nvim_get_mode().mode == 'i' then\n        if key == 'a' then\n            return ''\n        end\n    end\nend)\n```\n\n### z.lua will not trigger.\n```lua\nvim.api.nvim_buf_set_text(0, 0, 0, 0, 0, { 'aaa' })\n```\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\nnvim --clean\nsource x.lua\n\ntype a\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nDo not trigger the `CursorMovedI` and `TextChangedI` events.\n\n### Nvim version (nvim -v)\n\nNVIM v0.12.0-dev-400+gdc6885dc24\n\n### Vim (not Nvim) behaves the same?\n\nNo testing\n\n### Operating system/version\n\nWindows_NT 10.0.19045\n\n### Terminal name/version\n\nTerminal (Unpackaged) Version: 1.23.250314002-preview\n\n### $TERM environment variable\n\nxterm-256color\n\n### Installation\n\ngithub release unzip",
